Title: Slightly improved speed for cmk-update-config
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1667808747
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p30

The cmk-update-config program is used for transforming configurations between major versions.
In distributed setups, if the remote site is newer than the central site, this script has to be called on every activate changes.
This werk improves the transformation time of rulesets.
